    "• Similarly, Ong et al.'s (2020) study on STEM-based 5E inquiry learning models demonstrated the positive effects of these models on the teaching process.",
    "Nevertheless, research on different models in Chinese STEM education is scarce, highlighting the need for further investigation into alternative approaches and their effectiveness in various contexts.",
    "• Further research, including Lin et al. (2022b), has explored the competencies necessary for integrated STEM instruction in China.",
